<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4545172>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 56. Lateral views of the skull and lower jaw of (A) the holotype of Eptesicus andinus (AMNH 33807; male) and (B) E. chiriquinus from Paracou (AMNH 267234; male). Note the species difference in development of the sagittal crest. Scale bars = 10 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4545172/files/figure.png" .

